'''德揚·昌德'''（{{lang|en|Dhyan Chand}}，{{bd|1905年|8月29日|1979年|12月3日||}}），是[[印度|印度]][[曲棍球|曲棍球]]運動員，被廣泛認為是這項運動歷史上最偉大的。<ref name=Brittanica>{{cite web |url=http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/105366/Dhyan-Chand |work=Encyclopædia Britannica |title=Dhyan Chand (Indian athlete) |accessdate=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2015-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610215348/http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/105366/Dhyan-Chand |dead-url=no }}</ref>在1928年、1932年和1936年印度占曲棍球主導地位的年代裡，他除了獲得三枚奧運金牌外，還以出色的進球能力而聞名。在他的影響之下，印度在1928年至1964年的八屆奧運會中有七屆贏得了曲棍球比賽。

由於出色的控球能力，昌德被譽為曲棍球的巫師<ref>{{cite news|title=Find out about India's hockey wizard|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sportacademy/hi/sa/hockey/features/newsid_3493000/3493965.stm|website=bbc.co.uk|accessdate=2020-09-26|archive-date=2016-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160416173832/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sportacademy/hi/sa/hockey/features/newsid_3493000/3493965.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Dhyan Chand – The Legend Lives On |url=http://www.bharatiyahockey.org/granthalaya/legend/encounters/page12.htm |website=bhartiyahockey.org |accessdate=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2014-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141230074712/http://www.bharatiyahockey.org/granthalaya/legend/encounters/page12.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，或曲棍球的魔術師<ref>{{cite news |url=https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/sport-others/national-sports-day-pm-narendra-modi-pays-tribute-to-major-dhyan-chand-on-birth-anniversary-4818607/ |title=National Sports Day: PM Narendra Modi pays tribute to Major Dhyan Chand on birth anniversary |date=29 August 2017 |publisher=Indian Express |accessdate=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2018-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180724213316/https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/sport-others/national-sports-day-pm-narendra-modi-pays-tribute-to-major-dhyan-chand-on-birth-anniversary-4818607/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://sports.rediff.com/report/2010/aug/28/remembering-hockey-legend-dhyan-chand-magician.htm |title='Remembering Dhyan Chand, the magician' |date=28 August 2010 |publisher=rediff.com |accessdate=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2018-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180724214820/http://sports.rediff.com/report/2010/aug/28/remembering-hockey-legend-dhyan-chand-magician.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。根據他的自傳《進球》，他在1926年至1949年間的185場國際比賽攻入570個球。<ref>''Goal'', Chand, p. 255</ref>印度政府於1956年授予他印度第三級公民榮譽獎章[[蓮花裝勳章|蓮花裝勳章]]。<ref name="Padma Awards">{{cite web |url=http://mha.nic.in/sites/upload_files/mha/files/LST-PDAWD-2013.pdf |title=Padma Awards |publisher=Ministry of Home Affairs, Government of India |date=2015 |accessdate=21 July 2015 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015193758/http://mha.nic.in/sites/upload_files/mha/files/LST-PDAWD-2013.pdf |archivedate=15 October 2015}}</ref>他的生日是8月29日，被印度政府訂為「國家體育日」，每年都舉辦慶祝活動。

